The reason for the PRE-SQL usage is because the SQL being executed is a series of SQLs that use global temporary tables. NOTE The same session has been used 10 times for 10 different MODELs because MODEL and MODEL_TYP_CD are passed as parameters in PRE-SQL resulting in the population of TAPC_CLAIMS_STAGE build based on MODELs. All the 10 sessions use a single mapping m_Dummy_APC_MODEL_Build.

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Pre SQL
